description: Frontend architecture and feature separation rules
globs:
  - "app/**/*"
  - "features/**/*"
  - "shared/**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

# architecture.mdc

- Use feature-based architecture
- Keep shared code inside shared/
- Keep feature-specific logic inside features/
- Separate UI, business logic, and data access concerns
- Avoid putting business logic directly inside UI components
- Prefer services or actions for reusable business logic
- Keep components focused on presentation
- Keep files reasonably small and cohesive
- Avoid circular dependencies
- Prefer explicit boundaries between layers
- Favor maintainability over premature abstraction
- Avoid large monolithic components
- Colocate related files when it improves clarity